="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-hm-rt-itm cb-bg-white cb-ad-unit"> <div id="mpu2" class="ad-unit center-block"></div> </div> <div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-hm-rt-itm cb-bg-white"> <h4 class="cb-mdl-hdr">Specials</h4> <div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/135243/august-2025-news-digest" title="August 2025 - News Digest"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="August 2025 - News Digest" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c745297/tilak-varma-is-part-of-indias.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">August 2025 - News Digest</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">News bytes that you may have missed otherwise</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/135461/untethering-jitesh-sharma-india-asia-cup-2025" title="Untethering Jitesh Sharma"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Untethering Jitesh Sharma" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c745835/jitesh-sharma-will-hope-his-la.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Untethering Jitesh Sharma</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">Once weighed down by the India cap, the Vidarbha and RCB keeper-bat is now chasing freedom over fear</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/135394/cheteshwar-pujara-a-master-in-stillness" title="Cheteshwar Pujara: A master in stillness"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Cheteshwar Pujara: A master in stillness" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c742859/pujaras-legacy-lay-in-effecti.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Cheteshwar Pujara: A master in stillness</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">The legacy of the Test batter's storied career was beyond numbers. It lay in effectiveness, erosion and making batting tenacity sexy again</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/135161/shubman-of-the-series" title="Shubman of the series"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Shubman of the series" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c731513/hes-trying-to-keep-his-front.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Shubman of the series</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">Technique, temperament, and timing: how all finally fell in tune for Gill to have his fill</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/135046/india-cricket-tour-of-england-2025-crickets-willow-stretched-by-time-and-demand-anderson-tendulkar-trophy" title="Cricket's willow, stretched by time and demand"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Cricket's willow, stretched by time and demand" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c728866/the-t20-boom-has-driven-demand.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Cricket's willow, stretched by time and demand</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">As cricket's appetite for bats surges, the game's most sacred tree faces the game's growth, shorter growing cycles, and ecological strain</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134804/second-division-first-steps-back-karun-nairs-burbage-eaton-reboot" title="Second division, first steps back: Karun Nair's Burbage & Easton reboot"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Second division, first steps back: Karun Nair's Burbage & Easton reboot" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c721380/we-googled-him-said-jonath.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Second division, first steps back: Karun Nair's Burbage & Easton reboot</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">In search of a plan B, Karun Nair ended up in a second division club of the West of England Premier League, where he could clear his head and just play</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/135059/india-tour-of-england-2025-harry-brook-england-cricket-team" title="Odds on Harry Brook, the sure bet who is rolling the dice"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Odds on Harry Brook, the sure bet who is rolling the dice" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c729024/the-shift-from-the-boy-who-ba.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Odds on Harry Brook, the sure bet who is rolling the dice</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">England's rising star has had a journey marked by early faith, a steep rise, and technical challenges, and this India series, a curious mix of class and unpredictability, might just be another step in his evolution</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/135036/when-no-one-is-answerable-the-caribbeans-cricket-crisis" title="When no one is answerable: The Caribbean's cricket crisis"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="When no one is answerable: The Caribbean's cricket crisis" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c728651/how-does-a-sport-survive-when.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">When no one is answerable: The Caribbean's cricket crisis</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">How does a sport survive when administrators face no scrutiny, ignore results and remain in power year after year? </div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134848/indias-tour-of-england-2025-1st-test-leeds-headingley-ben-duckett-feature-reverse-engineered-how-duckett-became-a-sweeping-success" title="Reverse engineered: How Duckett became a sweeping success"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Reverse engineered: How Duckett became a sweeping success" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c722205/in-the-last-three-years-ducke.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Reverse engineered: How Duckett became a sweeping success</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">Few players in world cricket sweep as regularly or as effectively as Ben Duckett, who mastered the shot on both sides of the wicket from a young age</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134869/heinrich-klaasen-interview-mlc-2025-seattle-orcas-south-africa-international-retirement" title="Take bilateral ODIs away from international cricket - Heinrich Klaasen"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Take bilateral ODIs away from international cricket - Heinrich Klaasen" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c722835/heinrich-klaasen-believes-the.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Take bilateral ODIs away from international cricket - Heinrich Klaasen</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">The recently-retired South African opens up on his batting, his love-hate relationship with the game, the T20 World Cup heartbreak, the genius of Bumrah and a lot more</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134652/shubman-gill-takes-guard-at-the-dawn-of-indias-next-test" title="Shubman Gill takes guard at the dawn of India's next test"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Shubman Gill takes guard at the dawn of India's next test" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c716769/gill-is-indias-37th-test-capt.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Shubman Gill takes guard at the dawn of India's next test</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">The 25-year-old inherits India's Test captaincy at a time of sweeping change; his greatest challenge now is to lead while building the team he must lead</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134679/india-tour-of-england-2025-if-three-and-four-hold-a-fifth-can-strike-shubman-gill-rishabh-pant-karun-nair-sai-sudharsan" title="If three and four hold, a fifth can strike"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="If three and four hold, a fifth can strike" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c717486/the-challenge-for-india-now-is.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">If three and four hold, a fifth can strike</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">As India undergo a middle-order reset there is more at stake than runs and averages - the team's architecture relies on the success of Nos. 3 and 4</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134878/squire-mitchley-still-sparky-after-all-these-years" title="Squire Mitchley still sparky after all these years"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Squire Mitchley still sparky after all these years" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c723349/on-his-87th-birthday-cyril-mi.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Squire Mitchley still sparky after all these years</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">On his 87th birthday, Cyril Mitchley reflects on a life in cricket, his role in DRS history and the characters who shaped the game</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134342/virat-kohli-all-heart-full-tilt-test-cricket-tragic-india-cricket-test-retirement-king-kohli-feature-farewell" title="Virat Kohli: All heart, full tilt, Test cricket tragic"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Virat Kohli: All heart, full tilt, Test cricket tragic" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c692898/kohl-stripped-test-cricket-of.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Virat Kohli: All heart, full tilt, Test cricket tragic</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">Kohl stripped Test cricket of its ornamental restraint and dressed it in muscle and intent. He walked into hostile grounds with his collar turned up, demanded fast bowlers give "hell to opposition" and treated draws as a last resort</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134639/wtc-2025-final-going-where-no-south-african-has-been-before-temba-bavuma" title="Going where no South African has been before"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Going where no South African has been before" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c716541/temba-bavuma-led-south-africa.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Going where no South African has been before</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">How the magnitude of winning over the world finally sunk in at Lord's for Temba Bavuma's South Africa</div></div><div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-mid-wrp cb-pos-rel"><a href="/cricket-news/134659/south-africa-icc-wtc-champion-2025-lords-cricket" title="Finally, South Africa like what they see in the mirror"><img class="cb-vid-img lazy-loading" alt="Finally, South Africa like what they see in the mirror" source="https://static.cricbuzz.com/a/img/v1/300x170/i1/c716998/cricket-has-gone-and-won-somet.jpg" src="" height="170" width="303"/><h4 class="text-hvr-underline">Finally, South Africa like what they see in the mirror</h4></a><div class="cb-nws-intr">Cricket has gone and won something big. How might that change its relationship with South Africans?</div></div> </div> <div class="cb-col cb-col-100 cb-hm-rt-itm cb-bg-white cb-ad-unit"> <div id="mpu3" class="ad-unit center-block"></div> </div> </div> <script> CTEventName = "Screen View"; CTEventObj['Screen Name'] = "home";</script> <span id="skin_right" class="ad-unit" style="overflow:hidden;position:fixed;top:0;left:calc(50% + 490px);margin-left:3px;z-index:-99;"></span><div id="cb-plus-logout-msg" ng-controller ="CBPlusAuth" class="disp-none"></div></div></div><div ng-cloak ng-if='$root.$GEO.isGeo("EU")'><div class="feedback-bar text-center cb-col-100 disp-none feedback-menu" id="feedback-bar" ng-controller="FeedbackCtrl"	ng-init="show_feedback_menu();"><span class="feedback-t